{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation’s callout view."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","text":"MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"id<MLNAnnotation>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"annotation","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"UIControl","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)UIControl"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"control","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The map view containing the specified annotation.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The annotation whose accessory view was tapped.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"annotation"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The control that was tapped.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"control"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In a standard callout view, accessory views contain custom content and are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"positioned on either side of the annotation title text. If an accessory view"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you specify is a descendant of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class, the map view calls this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method as a convenience whenever the user taps your view. You can use this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method to respond to taps and perform any actions associated with that control."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, if your control displays additional information about the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotation, you could use this method to present a modal panel with that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your custom accessory views are not descendants of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIControl"},{"type":"text","text":" class,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the map view does not call this method. If the annotation has a custom callout"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"view via the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-mapView:calloutViewForAnnotation:"},{"type":"text","text":" method, you can specify the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"custom accessory views using the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNCalloutView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"leftAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rightAccessoryView"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples","anchor":"Related-examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Default callout usage, learn how to trigger an action when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"standard callout bubble’s accessory control is tapped."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","roleHeading":"Instance Method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L993","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:":{"title":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:annotation:calloutAccessoryControlTapped:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:annotation:calloutaccessorycontroltapped:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tells the delegate that the user tapped one of the accessory controls in the"},{"text":"